response.original_title: Rowan Atkinson: Not Just a Pretty Face
response.overview: Documentary celebrating the career of British comedian Rowan Atkinson, creator of beloved characters Mr. Bean and Edmund Blackadder. Explores his journey from electrical engineering student at Oxford to becoming one of Britain's most recognized comedic talents, featuring clips from his iconic performances and insights into his unique approach to physical comedy and character creation.
response.title: Rowan Atkinson: Not Just a Pretty Face
